  "content": "<div class=\"content-main relative\">\n <h1 class=\"block text-[4rem] text-[var(--dark)] leading-[4.4rem] font-semibold mb-[5px]\">Linh thi&ecirc;ng Lễ hội Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; Cam Đường</h1>\n <div class=\"content-meta flex items-center flex-wrap flex-row text-[1.3rem] leading-[2rem] font-normal text-[#999] truncate h-[30px] mb-[10px] [&amp;&gt;:not(:first-child)]:ml-[25px]\">\n  <div class=\"flex items-center\">\n   <a href=\"/bao-lao-cai-lao-cai-p438.epi\" class=\"bm-card-source flex items-center shrink-0\" title=\"B&aacute;o L&agrave;o Cai\">\n    <figure class=\"image opacity-80 w-auto h-[16px]\" style=\"width:48.75px;height:20px\" aria-label=\"Logo nh&agrave; xuất bản\">\n     <picture>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/262cb4d6c89b21c5788a.png\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n      <source srcset=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/262cb4d6c89b21c5788a.png\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n      <img src=\"https://photo-baomoi.bmcdn.me/262cb4d6c89b21c5788a.png\" alt=\"B&aacute;o L&agrave;o Cai\" width=\"78\" height=\"32\" />\n     </picture>\n    </figure></a>\n   <span><button class=\"relative text-[14px] leading-[normal] font-normal text-center cursor-pointer normal-case border-0 transition-button disabled:shadow-none disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed follow-button flex items-center item-star ml-[10px]\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" title=\"Theo d&otilde;i &quot;L&agrave;o Cai&quot;\" aria-label=\"Button\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-star text-[var(--primary)]\"></i></button></span>\n  </div>\n  <time datetime=\"2025-11-02T10:45:00.000Z\">8 giờ trước</time>\n  <a href=\"/tin-lien-quan-t41540063.epi\" class=\"related inline !text-[#adb5bd] hover:!text-[var(--primary)]\">1\n   <!-- --> li&ecirc;n quan</a>\n  <a href=\"/linh-thieng-le-hoi-den-doi-co-cam-duong-r53652951.epi\" class=\"origin item-origin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"></i><span>Gốc</span></a>\n  <i class=\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle bg-[0_-773px] w-[23px] h-[23px]\"></i>\n </div>\n <h3 class=\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\">S&aacute;ng 02/11 (tức ng&agrave;y 13/9 &acirc;m lịch), UBND phường Cam Đường, tỉnh L&agrave;o Cai tổ chức Lễ hội Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; năm 2025, sự kiện văn h&oacute;a, t&acirc;m linh c&oacute; &yacute; nghĩa s&acirc;u sắc, thu h&uacute;t đ&ocirc;ng đảo người d&acirc;n v&agrave; du kh&aacute;ch thập phương tham dự.</h3>\n <div class=\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [&amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-[15px]\">\n  <p class=\"text\">Tham dự lễ hội c&oacute; đồng ch&iacute; Dương Đức Huy - Ủy vi&ecirc;n Ban Thường vụ, Trưởng Ban Tuy&ecirc;n gi&aacute;o v&agrave; D&acirc;n vận Tỉnh ủy; l&atilde;nh đạo c&aacute;c sở, ban, ng&agrave;nh, x&atilde;, phường tr&ecirc;n địa b&agrave;n tỉnh c&ugrave;ng đ&ocirc;ng đảo Nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n v&agrave; du kh&aacute;ch thập phương.</p>\n  <div class=\"video-wrapper max-h-[80vh]\" style=\"width:625px;height:351.5625px;background:url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/player-default-03.png) no-repeat center center;background-size:cover\"></div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> To&agrave;n cảnh Lễ hội Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; Cam Đường năm 2025. </em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\" Lễ hội thu h&uacute;t đ&ocirc;ng đảo Nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n, du kh&aacute;ch . \" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> Lễ hội thu h&uacute;t đ&ocirc;ng đảo Nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n, du kh&aacute;ch . </em></p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; Cam Đường l&agrave; di t&iacute;ch lịch sử văn h&oacute;a cấp tỉnh, tọa lạc tại tổ 11 B&igrave;nh Minh, phường Cam Đường. Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; một trong những điểm tựa t&acirc;m linh, gắn liền với truyền t&iacute;ch về Nhị vị Th&aacute;nh C&ocirc;, được Nh&acirc;n d&acirc;n t&ocirc;n k&iacute;nh qua nhiều thế hệ. Qua h&agrave;ng trăm năm tồn tại, Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; vẫn giữ được vẻ trang nghi&ecirc;m, trở th&agrave;nh biểu tượng văn h&oacute;a đặc sắc, thể hiện đạo l&yacute; “Uống nước nhớ nguồn” của d&acirc;n tộc.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\" Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; Cam Đường thờ Nhị vị Th&aacute;nh C&ocirc;. \" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; Cam Đường thờ Nhị vị Th&aacute;nh C&ocirc;. </em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\" &Ocirc;ng Nguyễn Xu&acirc;n Nhẫn - Ph&oacute; B&iacute; thư Đảng ủy, Chủ tịch UBND phường Cam Đường đ&aacute;nh trống khai hội. \" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> &Ocirc;ng Nguyễn Xu&acirc;n Nhẫn - Ph&oacute; B&iacute; thư Đảng ủy, Chủ tịch UBND phường Cam Đường đ&aacute;nh trống khai hội. </em></p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\" B&agrave; Nguyễn Thu Ho&agrave;i - Ph&oacute; Chủ tịch UBND phường Cam Đường, Trưởng Ban tổ chức Lễ hội ph&aacute;t biểu khai mạc. \" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text media-caption text-center text-[18px] leading-[24px]\"><em> B&agrave; Nguyễn Thu Ho&agrave;i - Ph&oacute; Chủ tịch UBND phường Cam Đường, Trưởng Ban tổ chức Lễ hội ph&aacute;t biểu khai mạc. </em></p>\n  <p class=\"text\">Lễ hội Đền Đ&ocirc;i C&ocirc; năm 2025, diễn ra với chuỗi hoạt động văn h&oacute;a phong ph&uacute;, gồm: Lễ tế ch&iacute;nh giỗ Nhị vị Th&aacute;nh C&ocirc;; lễ d&acirc;ng hương; biểu diễn h&aacute;t then, h&aacute;t quan họ, chầu văn, hầu đồng mang đậm bản sắc d&acirc;n gian; lễ tạ, ph&aacute;t lộc Th&aacute;nh C&ocirc; ban, cầu cho mưa thuận gi&oacute; h&ograve;a, quốc th&aacute;i d&acirc;n an, nh&acirc;n khang vật thịnh.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:350px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"350\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-sta